        "description": "Grounding source information for the message.\n\nDiscriminated by `source_type`:\n- `case_file`: Source is a file attached to the case. Has `case_id` and `file_id`.\n- `hub`: Source is a file from a hub. Has `hub_id` and `file_id` (or legacy `entity_id`).\n- `project`: Source is from a project property (legacy). Has `project_id`, `property_id`, `entity_id`.\n- `web_search`: Source is from web search results. Has `web_references`.\n",
