        "description": "Enable trigger request. Can specify:\n- `{\"provider\": \"pipedream\", \"provider_metadata\": {...}}` - Set Pipedream provider\n- `{\"provider\": \"other\"}` - Set other/custom provider\n- `{}` - Preserve existing provider configuration (empty body)\n\n@deprecated Use SetupSourceRequest instead.\n",
