      "Projects.PropertyResponse": {
        "additionalProperties": false,
        "description": "A property",
        "properties": {
          "config": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Projects.PropertyConfigResponse"
          },
          "description": {
            "description": "Property description. Can contain input references in the format `@<input.reference_as>` or hub references in the format `@<hub.reference_as>`.\n\nThe `reference_as` field uniquely identifies an input or hub and follows these patterns:\n\n**Input References:**\n- `P<property_id>` - for value inputs from properties (target: value)\n- `P<property_id>:E<entity_id>` - for value inputs from library properties\n- `P<property_id>:T<input_target>` - for targeted inputs (e.g., metadata, sub-path extraction)\n- `P<property_id>:T<input_target>[key=val,...]` - for targeted inputs with dynamic filters\n- `P<property_id>:E<entity_id>:T<input_target>` - for targeted inputs from library properties\n\n**Sub-path Targets (for bundle properties):**\n- `:Tvalue.text` - extracts the text portion from a bundle as a text input\n- `:Tvalue.files` - extracts all files from a bundle as file inputs\n- `:Tvalue.files[category=output]` - extracts files filtered by category\n- `:Tvalue.files[filename=report.pdf]` - extracts files filtered by filename\n- `:Tvalue.files[category=output,filename=report.pdf]` - combined filter\n\n**Metadata Targets:**\n- `:Ttool_metadata.motivation` - extracts tool motivation metadata\n- `:Ttool_metadata.confidence` - extracts tool confidence metadata\n\n**Hub References:**\n- `H<hub_id>` - for direct hub references (static hubs, i.e. hubs not from hub select properties)\n- For hubs from hub select properties, use the property's `reference_as` (e.g., `P<property_id>`)\n\nExamples:\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f>` - reference to property value\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f:E01i9w5n4-0g3b-5c6d-9f8e-2b3c4d5e6f7g>` - reference to library property value\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f:Ttool_metadata.motivation>` - reference to property metadata\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f:Tvalue.text>` - reference to bundle text extraction\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f:Tvalue.files[category=output]>` - reference to filtered bundle files\n- `@<H01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f>` - direct reference to a static hub by its ID\n",
            "nullable": true,
            "type": "string"
          },
          "effective_tool": {
            "deprecated": true,
            "description": "Deprecated: always set to `tool`",
            "type": "string"
          },
          "enabled_skills": {
            "default": [],
            "description": "List of skills enabled for this property (only available for non-manual properties)",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Projects.EnabledSkill"
            },
            "type": "array"
          },
          "hash": {
            "nullable": false,
            "type": "string"
          },
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Common.UUID"
          },
          "incomplete_collection_input_rows_behaviour": {
            "enum": [
              "never",
              "drop_on_any_errors",
              "drop_any_incomplete",
              "drop_on_any_entity_errors"
            ],
            "type": "string"
          },
          "input_ids": {
            "deprecated": true,
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Common.UUID"
            },
            "type": "array"
          },
          "inputs": {
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Projects.PropertyInputResponse"
            },
            "type": "array"
          },
          "is_grounded": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "owner": {
            "enum": [
              "user",
              "system"
            ],
            "type": "string"
          },
          "parent_project_id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Common.NullableUUID"
          },
          "parent_property_id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Common.NullableUUID"
          },
          "remote_outputs": {
            "description": "List of all outputs for that property that are not located in current project.\n`active` field is set to true if that property fields will be recalculated or\nmarked as stale if fields of this property change. Generally, this should be almost\nalways the case, but sometimes you may see `active` set to false if property has\ntoo many dependencies.\n",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Projects.PropertyRemoteOutputResponse"
            },
            "type": "array"
          },
          "reviewable": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "skip_behaviour": {
            "enum": [
              "never",
              "on_unsupported_input",
              "on_all_unsupported_inputs"
            ],
            "type": "string"
          },
          "slug": {
            "pattern": "^[a-z_-][a-z0-9_-]*$",
            "type": "string"
          },
          "supported_indices": {
            "items": {
              "enum": [
                "semantic"
              ],
              "type": "string"
            },
            "type": "array"
          },
          "tool": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Projects.Common.PropertyTool"
          },
          "tool_config": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Projects.PropertyToolConfig"
          },
          "tool_version": {
            "nullable": true,
            "type": "string"
          },
          "type": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Projects.Common.PropertyType"
          },
          "visible_in_entity_sidebar": {
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "id",
          "name",
          "slug",
          "description",
          "type",
          "tool",
          "is_grounded",
          "input_ids",
          "inputs",
          "owner",
          "hash",
          "skip_behaviour",
          "incomplete_collection_input_rows_behaviour",
          "tool_config",
          "visible_in_entity_sidebar",
          "reviewable",
          "remote_outputs",
          "enabled_skills"
        ],
        "title": "Projects.PropertyResponse",
        "type": "object"
      },
