      "Projects.InputReference": {
        "description": "Input reference that can be used in property descriptions and skill argument overrides.\n\nCan contain input references in the format `@<input.reference_as>` or hub references in the format `@<hub.reference_as>`.\n\nThe `reference_as` field uniquely identifies an input or hub and follows these patterns:\n\n**Input References:**\n- `P<property_id>` - for value inputs from properties (target: value)\n- `P<property_id>:E<entity_id>` - for value inputs from library properties\n- `P<property_id>:T<input_target>` - for targeted inputs (e.g., metadata, sub-path extraction)\n- `P<property_id>:T<input_target>[key=val,...]` - for targeted inputs with dynamic filters\n- `P<property_id>:E<entity_id>:T<input_target>` - for targeted inputs from library properties\n\n**Sub-path Targets (for bundle properties):**\n- `:Tvalue.text` - extracts the text portion from a bundle as a text input\n- `:Tvalue.files` - extracts all files from a bundle as file inputs\n- `:Tvalue.files[category=output]` - extracts files filtered by category\n- `:Tvalue.files[filename=report.pdf]` - extracts files filtered by filename\n- `:Tvalue.files[category=output,filename=report.pdf]` - combined filter\n\n**Metadata Targets:**\n- `:Ttool_metadata.motivation` - extracts tool motivation metadata\n- `:Ttool_metadata.confidence` - extracts tool confidence metadata\n\n**Hub References:**\n- `H<hub_id>` - for direct hub references (static hubs, i.e. hubs not from hub select properties)\n- For hubs from hub select properties, use the property's `reference_as` (e.g., `P<property_id>`)\n\nExamples:\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f>` - reference to property value\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f:E01i9w5n4-0g3b-5c6d-9f8e-2b3c4d5e6f7g>` - reference to library property value\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f:Ttool_metadata.motivation>` - reference to property metadata\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f:Tvalue.text>` - reference to bundle text extraction\n- `@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f:Tvalue.files[category=output]>` - reference to filtered bundle files\n- `@<H01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f>` - direct reference to a static hub by its ID\n",
        "example": "@<P01h8v4k3-9f2a-4b5c-8e7d-1a2b3c4d5e6f>",
        "pattern": "^@<[[:alnum:]_.:\\-\\[\\]=,]+>$",
        "title": "Projects.InputReference",
        "type": "string"
      },
