    "/api/workspaces/{workspace_id}/projects/{project_id}/triggers/inbound/{inbound_trigger_id}/source": {
      "post": {
        "callbacks": {},
        "description": "Sets up the trigger source (provider configuration) and activates the trigger.\n\nWhen enabled, webhooks create entities in the backing project automatically.\n\n## Provider Configuration Options\n\n1. **Pipedream source**: `{\"provider\": \"pipedream\", \"provider_metadata\": {...}}`\n   - Requires `component_key`, `configured_props`, and `integration_connection_id`\n   - `dynamic_props_id` is optional (nullable)\n   - Automatically deploys trigger to Pipedream\n   - If a trigger is already deployed, it will be removed and redeployed\n\n2. **Other/Custom source**: `{\"provider\": \"other\"}`\n   - No metadata required for custom webhooks\n",
        "operationId": "inbound-trigger-setup-source",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "description": "",
            "in": "path",
            "name": "workspace_id",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Common.UUID"
            }
